<p>
<b>Not implemented:</b>
<p>
<ul>
<li>particles algorithm has not been changed from prototype
<li>no bars in bar graph
<li>no tick marks on bar graph
<li>pH slider scale doesn't line up with bar graph
<li>linear and log scale options for bar graph don't work
<li>no zoom buttons for linear graph
<li>layout and "look" of molecule counts is not as shown in design doc
<li>a small subset of liquids is provided
<li>liquid color does not change when diluted with water
</ul>
<p>
<b>Know issues:</b>
<p>
<ul>
<li>molecule counts are hard to see when "ratio" view is on
</ul>
